media:group.media:title: S.T.A.L.K.E.R. CoP #15 - Secret Weapons
media:group.media:description:
With new information from Cardan, we head down to a previously sealed underground testing facility, before returning to Pripyat to explore the dark, haunted streets.
Check out the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/41700/STALKER_Call_of_Pripyat/
